usage: git bundler [<options>] [--] [<bundle-path>...]

Register bundle path in global zou-flow config file (~/.zou-flow)
or/and list registered bundles

    -h|--help               display help
    -u|--unregister         unregister bundle path
    -s|--scan               scan and register bundles that are siblings of zou.
    <bundle-path>...        bundle path
    
example:
    git bundler                     # register current bundle
    git bundler -s                  # register zou's sibling bundles
    git bundler -u                  # unregister current bundle
    git bundler -- bundle1 bundle2  # register bundle1 and bundle2 pathes
